## 6. Comparative Complexity

**OpenAI Provider** (Multi-capability):
- 21 source files in src directory
- Supports 6 different model types (chat, completion, embedding, image, speech, transcription)
- ~400 lines in main provider, 350 lines in image model
- Complex option handling across multiple APIs

**LMNT Provider** (Single-capability):
- 10 source files in src directory
- Supports only speech synthesis
- ~84 lines in provider, 209 lines in speech model
- Focused, minimal API surface

