## 7. Key Files Summary

| File Path | Purpose | Size |
|-----------|---------|------|
| `/packages/openai/package.json` | NPM metadata, dependencies | 84 lines |
| `/packages/openai/src/openai-provider.ts` | Factory, main export point | 271 lines |
| `/packages/openai/src/image/openai-image-model.ts` | Image generation implementation | 350 lines |
| `/packages/openai/src/image/openai-image-api.ts` | Response schema validation | 36 lines |
| `/packages/lmnt/src/lmnt-provider.ts` | Minimal speech provider | 84 lines |
