This comprehensive structure allows the SDK to:
1. Support multiple AI providers with consistent interfaces
2. Enable easy addition of new providers by following patterns
3. Share common utilities and validation
4. Maintain backwards compatibility through versioning (v2, v3)
5. Provide type-safe, validated interactions with external APIs

